author: bruno
msg: Uncomment the container-encoding and form-encoding parameters, this
makes no difference as they otherwise also default to ISO-8859-1.
This makes it easier to replace them using xpatch.
Add some clarification to the often-confused container-encoding.

author: bruno
msg: To have consistent encoding-behaviour between normal requests and
multipart requests, the container encoding should be used for decoding
